member.summary:
Contains the same fields as  parameters, and can be used instead of it.
These codes are equivalent:
Wnd w = Wnd.Find(a, b, c, d, e); if(!w.Is0) Print(w);
var p = new Wnd.FindParams(a, b, c, d, e); if(p.Find()) Print(p.Result);
Also can find in a custom list of windows.

